-- Deutsche Bank Hired to Assess Virgin Atlantic, Telegraph Says
-- B y   B e n   M a r t i n
-- 2010-11-05T02:51:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-05/deutsche-bank-hired-to-assess-virgin-atlantic-telegraph-says.html
Richard Branson  has hired  Deutsche
Bank AG  to assess Virgin Atlantic Airways Ltd.’s market position
following  British Airways Plc ’s tie-up with American Airlines,
the  Daily Telegraph reported , citing an unnamed person.  Options include Branson selling down his stake in the
company, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
